=== test.172: disable upstream root-port ASPM/CLKPM before test.171 post-fw idle probes — stage=0 ===
Date: Mon Apr 20 16:51:27 BST 2026

Stage 0: skip_arm=1 — test.162 scope + download_fw_nvram: enter_download_state (read-only) + BAR2 ioread32 probe + 442KB iowrite32 fw + NVRAM write + TCM verify dump; returns -ENODEV.
(test.172: test.171 completed the full 442KB fw write, logged idle-0 and idle-1 with ARM halted, then hard-froze before idle-2. This run disables ASPM/CLKPM on the upstream root port before download while preserving the same 10 x mdelay(10)+ARM-probe idle loop. Expected: survival through post-idle-loop implicates root-port link power management; another freeze after idle-1 shifts focus to chip PMU/watchdog or BAR0 probe side effects.)

